modules.description: Provides property-based testing combinators for OUnit, enabling the execution of randomized test cases against functions that take and return arbitrary values. Operates with functions that generate and check properties, using custom generators and printers for complex data types. Used to validate invariants in data transformation pipelines and ensure correctness under varied input conditions.

Converts QCheck tests into OUnit and OUnit2 test formats, supporting randomization and detailed output. Handles test lists and integrates with command-line arguments for seed control. Executes tests with compact or TAP-compatible reporting, capturing failures and errors with contextual details.
